At that time the venerable elder mother of lord minister of Halu Dyah Sahasra offered gifts:
	- to his majesty the king: 5 suvarṇas, 1 pair of cloth as royal reward
	- to the Hino: 2 suvarṇas, 8 māṣas, 1 pair of royal jaro cloth
	- to the lord minister of Halu Dyah Sahasra: 1 suvarṇa, 4 māṣas, 1 pair of cloth
