	- the Akudur Pu Tunaṅ: 1 suvarṇa, 4 māṣas, 1 pair of cloth
	- the Maṅhuri Pu Paṇḍamuan: 10 māṣas, 1 pair of cloth
	- the Halaran Pu Bhāmā: 10 māṣas, 1 pair of cloth
